00:07:39,080 --> 00:07:40,930
This is the home address of Chief Ohashi

135
00:07:40,930 --> 00:07:42,530
and his schedule these days.

136
00:07:46,390 --> 00:07:47,460
This time,

137
00:07:47,490 --> 00:07:48,960
we must make Chief Ohashi

138
00:07:48,980 --> 00:07:51,500
a dead person on the file of the NBIS.

